---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
// Aca importaremos los componentes después
---

<Layout
  title="Tane Solution | Diseño Web para PYMES"
  description="Diseñamos páginas a medida, sin plantillas, y nos ocupamos de toda la parte técnica para que tú solo te enfoques en atender a tus nuevos clientes."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
      class="relative pt-12 pb-16 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden min-h-[85vh] flex items-center"
    >
      <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
        <img
          src="/images/tane_hero_branded.png"
          alt="Tane Solutions Corporate Background"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-slate-900/40 via-slate-900/80 to-slate-950"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center max-w-6xl relative z-10"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 backdrop-blur-sm text-sm text-brand font-medium mb-8"
        >
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand"></span>
          Agencia nº1 en Diseño Web para Negocios Reales
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8"
        >
          Consigue la página web <br />que tu negocio necesita:<br />
          <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-brand to-brand/80"
            >Rápida, Profesional y Diseñada para Atraer Clientes.</span
          >
        </h1>

        <p
          class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
          Tu negocio local no debería ser un secreto.<br /> Olvídate de plantillas
          baratas y procesos técnicos interminables.<br /> Diseñamos tu web a medida
          en tiempo récord.
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4"
        >
          <a
            href="#precios"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-brand hover:bg-brand/90 text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_40px_-10px_rgba(217,255,0,0.3)]"
          >
            👉 Quiero mi web profesional
          </a>
          <a
            href="#demos"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all"
          >
            Ver ejemplos
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-400"
        >
          <div class="flex -space-x-2">
            <!-- Simulated avatars -->
            <div
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-xs"
            >
              J
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-600 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-xs"
            >
              M
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-500 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-xs"
            >
              S
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-400 ml-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              ><path
                d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              ><path
                d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              ><path
                d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              ><path
                d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              ><path
                d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <span>Proceso rápido y sin dolores de cabeza.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Agitación del Problema -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16">
          ¿Te suena familiar alguna de estas historias?
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div
            class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-8 rounded-2xl"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand/20 text-brand/40 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">
              "Mi web actual es de 2010"
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Tus clientes te buscan en Google, ven una web lenta,
              desactualizada o directamente fea, y se van a la competencia que
              transmite más confianza.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-8 rounded-2xl"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
                ></path><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">
              "Intenté hacerla yo mismo..."
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Pasaste horas peleándote con tutoriales de YouTube o Wix para
              darte cuenta de que no tienes tiempo para eso y el resultado no
              transmite tu calidad.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-8 rounded-2xl"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">
              "Agencias que tardan meses"
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Has pedido presupuestos y te hablan con tecnicismos, te piden
              precios desorbitados y te dan plazos de entrega que parecen un
              chiste.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-xl text-slate-300 mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Tu página web no debería ser un dolor de cabeza ni un pozo de gastos
          inútil. Debería ser <span class="text-brand font-bold"
            >tu mejor trabajador: disponible 24/7 para convencer a tus clientes.</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Beneficios -->
    <section id="beneficios" class="py-24 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2" data-reveal="left">
            <div
              class="relative w-full aspect-square md:aspect-video lg:aspect-square bg-slate-800/40 rounded-3xl border border-slate-700/50 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-8"
            >
              <!-- Grid Background -->
              <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#ffffff05_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#ffffff05_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-size-[32px_32px]"
              >
              </div>

              <!-- Floating UI Elements: Concept Mockup -->
              <div
                class="relative w-full max-w-md h-full flex items-center justify-center scale-90 sm:scale-100"
              >
                <!-- Main Card: "Performance & Quality" -->
                <div
                  class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative z-10 animate-[float_6s_ease-in-out_infinite] w-48 sm:w-64"
                >
                  <div
                    class="h-8 bg-slate-800/80 border-b border-slate-700 flex items-center px-4 gap-2"
                  >
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div>
                    <div
                      class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold"
                    >
                      Rendimiento
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 text-center">
                    <div
                      class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                    >
                      <svg
                        class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-24 sm:h-24 transform -rotate-90"
                        viewBox="0 0 96 96"
                      >
                        <circle
                          cx="48"
                          cy="48"
                          r="40"
                          stroke="currentColor"
                          stroke-width="8"
                          fill="transparent"
                          class="text-slate-800"></circle>
                        <circle
                          cx="48"
                          cy="48"
                          r="40"
                          stroke="currentColor"
                          stroke-width="8"
                          fill="transparent"
                          stroke-dasharray="251.2"
                          stroke-dashoffset="0"
                          class="text-brand"></circle>
                      </svg>
                      <span
                        class="absolute text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white"
                        >100</span
                      >
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="text-[12px] sm:text-sm font-medium text-slate-300"
                    >
                      Optimización Web
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Card: "Custom Branding" (Top Right) -->
                <div
                  class="absolute -right-4 -top-8 w-28 sm:-right-4 sm:-top-4 sm:w-44 bg-slate-800/90 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 shadow-xl z-20 animate-[float_7s_ease-in-out_infinite_1s]"
                >
                  <div
                    class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] text-brand font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2"
                  >
                    Ajustes de Diseño
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex gap-1.5 sm:gap-2 mb-3">
                    <div
                      class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 rounded-full bg-brand ring-2 ring-white/20"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500">
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500"
                    >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1 sm:space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="w-full h-1 sm:h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div>
                    <div class="w-4/5 h-1 sm:h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Card: "Managed Services" (Bottom Left) -->
                <div
                  class="absolute -left-4 -bottom-8 w-36 sm:-left-8 sm:-bottom-4 sm:w-52 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 shadow-xl z-20 animate-[float_5s_ease-in-out_infinite_2s]"
                >
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2 sm:mb-3">
                    <div
                      class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase"
                    >
                      Gestión Técnica
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="flex h-1.5 w-1.5 sm:h-2 sm:w-2 rounded-full bg-brand animate-pulse"
                    >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1.5 sm:space-y-2.5">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2">
                      <svg
                        class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 text-brand"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        ><path
                          stroke-linecap="round"
                          stroke-linejoin="round"
                          stroke-width="3"
                          d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                      >
                      <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-[11px] text-slate-300"
                        >SSL Activo</span
                      >
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2">
                      <svg
                        class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 text-brand"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        ><path
                          stroke-linecap="round"
                          stroke-linejoin="round"
                          stroke-width="3"
                          d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                      >
                      <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-[11px] text-slate-300"
                        >Backups</span
                      >
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2">
                      <svg
                        class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 text-brand"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        ><path
                          stroke-linecap="round"
                          stroke-linejoin="round"
                          stroke-width="3"
                          d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                      >
                      <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-[11px] text-slate-300"
                        >Cloud Hosting</span
                      >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-10">
              Diseño a medida, resultados reales y cero dolores de cabeza
              técnicos.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div
                  class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 text-brand flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    ><path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
                  >
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">
                    Construcción Ultra Rápida
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">
                    Lanzamos tu web en tiempo récord. Sin esperas interminables
                    que estancan tu lanzamiento.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div
                  class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 text-brand flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    ><path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"
                    ></path></svg
                  >
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">100% Personalizado</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">
                    Nada de plantillas genéricas. Tu negocio es único y
                    diseñamos tu marca para que destaque por encima de tu
                    competencia local.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div
                  class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 text-brand flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    ><path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
                    ></path><path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg
                  >
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Gestión Llave en Mano</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">
                    Dominamos toda la tecnología. Hosting, SEO base,
                    velocidad... nosotros lo dejamos resuelto. Tú solo apruebas
                    el resultado y cobras a tus clientes.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Demos / Portfolio -->
    <section id="demos" class="py-24 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
            Echa un vistazo a lo que podemos crear para ti
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            No importa tu sector, adaptamos la estrategia y el diseño a lo que
            tus clientes reales están buscando.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Demo 1 -->
          <a href="/demos/clinica-dental" class="group cursor-pointer block">
            <div
              class="relative w-full aspect-4/3 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-4 border border-slate-700 shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-2 group-hover:border-brand/50"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/dental_cover.png"
                alt="Demo Clínica Dental"
                class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
              />
